            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Thermas maiores <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> II <expan><abbr>adi</abbr><ex>utricis</ex></expan> Claudianae <lb n="3"/><supplied reason="lost">ma</supplied>gno tempore in<lb break="no" n="4"/><supplied reason="lost">te</supplied>rmissas et dest&amp;lt;i=L&amp;gt;tutas <lb n="5"/><supplied reason="lost">re</supplied>tracatis porticibus <lb n="6"/><supplied reason="lost">a</supplied>ditibusque <supplied reason="lost">pri</supplied>us refeci<supplied reason="lost">t</supplied> <lb n="7"/>exhiberi inde <supplied reason="lost">inc</supplied>episse <lb n="8"/><expan><abbr>militib</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> <supplied reason="lost">iuss</supplied>it <supplied reason="lost">pri</supplied>die <expan><abbr>Kal</abbr><ex>endas</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Iuli</abbr><ex>as</ex></expan> <lb n="9"/>praes<supplied reason="lost">id</supplied>e <supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>pr</abbr><ex>ovinciae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>e</abbr><ex>gregio</ex></expan></supplied> <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>iro</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Clemen</abbr><ex>tio</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Silvi</abbr><ex>no</ex></expan> <lb n="10"/>et cura <expan><abbr>Aur</abbr><ex>eli</ex></expan> Frontini pra<lb break="no" n="11"/><expan><abbr>ef</abbr><ex>ecti</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> eiusdem Pater<lb break="no" n="12"/>no II et Mariniano co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ulibus</ex></expan> 
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Die heute sichtbare Inschrift steht auf den Resten einer kaum noch lesbaren Vorgängerinschrift (TitAq 0160; 1. H. 3. Jh. n. Chr.). Angegebenes Datum (1.7.268): terminus post quem.</p>
